# My Book System Config

This guide teaches how to configure a MyBook server that is running Ubuntu 16.04.

## Config Files

ReadMe - This doc describing setup

Gunicorn - Web server configuration - /etc/systemd/system/gunicorn.service

    gunicorn.P.orig, gunicorn.P.1 

Nginx - Web server configuration - /etc/nginx/sites-available/django

    nginx.P.orig, nginx.P.1, nginx.P.2     
    nginx.S.orig, nginx.S.1, nginx.S.2   

Command Script

    x.py - This command script is executed as root to update system files

    usage:  ./x.py  command

        gunicorn
        nginx
        set-gunicorn
        set-nginx

Cron    
    cron.P - Configure to cron to renew SSL  - Paste to execute

